# =============================================================================
# Trio-based association models for ASD phenotypes
# =============================================================================
#
# Description:
# This script evaluates direct offspring and indirect parental polygenic score
# effects on ASD-related quantitative and binary phenotypes. Discovery and
# replication results are combined using fixed-effect meta-analysis, followed by
# publication-ready visualization.
#
# Notes:
# - Replace the file paths below with your own local or project paths.
# - The input files should contain sample-level phenotype, PGS, ancestry PC,
#   sex, ASD status, and keep-filter information.
# - The analysis logic is unchanged from the original working script.
# =============================================================================


